1) Create a springboot project which store the message data in to mongo db
Input:
Auto message communication :
Message: to,from,content,corelationid(int)

Output:

Operation:
Get
Post
Put
Delete

Run and test through curl and postman

2)Create Springboot microservice with mysql

Create a springboot project which store the message data in to mysql db
Input:
Auto message communication :

Message: to,from,content,corelationid(Int)

Operation:
Get: Read
Post: save
Put: Update message content
Delete: delete message from database

Run and test through curl and postman


Create the docker image for both application and test with database.

